name: This Cat Does Not Exist
desc: A website that uses AI to generate a cat that has never been seen before. Every time you visit, it generates a new cat.

name: Archive.org: Internet Archive
desc: Archive.org has the Wayback Machine, which archives webpages and is really helpful for finding a snapshot of a site that isn't available anymore, or doesn't work anymore. It also has an archive of free books, movies, software, etc.

name: Butter
desc: This one is not a website, just an album on imgur of knockoffs of 'I Can't Believe it's not Butter!'. It makes me laugh every time I look at it.
